103
00:26:41,000 --> 00:27:00,000
And one of the ways to do that is essentially to soup up that virus. You know, you can through genetic editing, you can make it more infectious and see if it is, you know, one of these things that it's a determination of where we should put our resources.

104
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:19,000
