121
00:31:53,000 --> 00:32:08,000
I believe the direct quote from Francis Collins, neither NIH nor NIAID have ever approved any grant that would have supported gain-of-function research on coronaviruses that would have increased their transmissibility or lethality for humans.

122
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:26,000
