135
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:51,000
So that is the goal of Eco Health Alliance. But the organization was pushing very, very hard for big funding dollars, not just to fund, you know, this research on a small scale, but had their eyes on something called the global viral project, which was basically a massive mapping of the world's viral strains.

136
00:36:51,000 --> 00:37:19,000
