155
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:57,000
And even though he's saying that he has no conflicts of interest, he was providing money to the Wuhan Institute of Virology.

156
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:07,000
So it was not a kind of neutral value free assertion, right? He has a stake in this. He definitely has a stake in this.

157
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:23,000
As somebody pointed out, you know, if it turns out to have been a lab leak, it could do to the field of virology what Chernobyl did to the world of nuclear science research, right?

158
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:28,000
Transform the whole thing, shutdowns, restrictions, moratoriums.

159
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:45,000
So Peter Daschak as the recipient of million, well, not personally, but EcoHealth Alliance as the recipient of millions of dollars in grant money definitely had, you know, a horse in this race.

160
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:52,000
Besides NIH, who else would be funding this type of research? Would the DOD be funding any of this research?

161
00:42:52,000 --> 00:43:18,000
It has. DOD gave grants to EcoHealth Alliance, you know, and so as I spoke with investigators inside the U.S. government who were looking at COVID origins over the last year, what they found is that there is a big, they called it gain of function bureaucracy inside the federal government.

162
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:34,000
There are a lot of people who are invested in this kind of research, who are giving grant money for this kind of research. So they, you know, they have committed to this kind of very aggressive viral research.

163
00:43:35,000 --> 00:43:53,000
And so they have, you know, an interest in the outcome of this question. And as these investigators told me, it had an enormous impact on their ability to just neutrally evaluate the question of origin.

164
00:43:54,000 --> 00:44:18,000
This is more of a question of speculation, but do you think that had all of this taken place in a world where it had not been politicized? In other words, if politicians, including the President of the United States had never weighed in on this, if this were a discussion that were only going to take place in the scientific community, do you think the reaction would have been as polarizing?

165
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:39,000
